             Submitting plagiarized or unoriginal work.<br>
             Failing to meet the submission deadline or format requirements.<br>
             Exceeding the team size limit (2–4 members).<br>
             Violating the code of conduct or event-specific guidelines.
          </p>
          <h3>Safety Measures :-</h3>
